title: I am looking for high elo players to play with (normals or ranked)
body:
I believe that for me to improve, I should be playing with players of higher calibre than myself.

Maybe even a high level team to take me under their wing and train me.

I am available all day every day for now

ign: whitepumah

replies.body: Feel free to join https://discord.gg/Y93kJJN, If you are interested in finding competitive league players.
